posts.title: Fucking bullshit, had to fire the useless roofers today...
posts.content:
So today me and my brother had enough. These mfs were contracted over 5 months ago, and all they had to do was work on the roof of this house we have been remodeling from top to bottom for the last 7 months, a shit ton of work has gone through this house, like the previous ones, cause we don't fuck around.

For those who don't know yet, I own a carpentry business with my brother, and 5 other employees which are awesome, these roofers are a separate entity that I contracted to work on the roof of this bullshit house which had a lot of serious problems, the crew of course, were nothing but Mexicans, the owner isn't, but the crew is, which is dumb, our previous roofers were American, and we never had issues, but this time we couldn't get em cause they have too much work already.

These mfs had a shit ton if time to fix, repair and finish the fucking roof, lots of call offs "oh, we can't show up this week, or this week, blah blah", and when they did show up, all they did was work for a little bit while playing bullshit Mexican music from their dirty ass stereo.

Meanwhile, we are fucking hustling, and trying to get everything done. Me and my brother went to Shot Show 2025, and I left Jake be in charge of the crew, he is fantastic at the job, 25 year old too, they're all down to earth and love to break balls, they have said I look like a bigger version of Baldur from "Gods of wars", I know who Baldur is, but never heard of Gods of wars. Some movie I think, and they drink after the day is done.

The roofers were supposed to show up when we were out in Vegas, and fix/finish the roof, there is a massive leak in the fucking master bedroom, which is causing problems.

While in Vegas, Jake calls me and says they didn't show up, I get fucking red. Today, we arrive at 7:30am, my crew is already there, working. First thing I ask is about the roof, I already knew the fucking answer, I start yapping around, and everyone is trying to calm me down, my brother gets frustrated as well.

THESE FUCKERS COME IN AT 10AM, approaching my trailer while speaking Spanish to tell me they are here to "finish the job".

I loose my shit, and immediately tell the faggots to fuck off, they are done, fireeeed. They loose their shit too, and start threatening me and my brother, calling us "putos", "stupid european gringos" and racists.

Now my brother is 6'5 foot, 260lbs, he may be a drinker, but the mf can clear an entire football field if he wanted to, so he approaches them and tell them to leave, the short faggots gang up on him, when I see this, oh, fucking reeeeeeddd, I pick up my hatchet and jump out of the trailer like fucking Spiderman.

They keep threatening us, my crew all come out and start to de-escalate, they start getting in their shitbox truck, I'm about to throw my fucking hatchet when my goofy ass brother shouts "DEI HIRES!!"

My crew start to laugh, I calm down and walk back to my mobile trailer, and they leave.

Anyways, now we have to finish the roof ourselves, posted this here cause I feel like it's a funny story and whatnot.
